      <title>The Sony ICF-2001D (ICF-2010) is a piece of Cold War espionage history. Released...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DVl3A0pDLkz/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/649511647_2581668275562796_4270578688493732872_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_p360x360_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=102&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg0NzcyMzQwNTczOTM0MjEzMQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjY0MHgxMTM2LnNkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=-rMAEJTZBb8Q7kNvwFhORNw&amp;_nc_oc=Ado2uIGeV5n3bOBcieA5Av5ZHDglJHHt-h7T88WAdyntGrZIgiU4ShmnB0Kzv8vK3Gw&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=lUCi0V0oIzZL0N8geRpueQ&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyTK6tysEWSft9EQsG-N52kBkHQVsCgncWBtBE7aVt4iw&amp;oe=69C9B824" alt="Instagram billede fra @technostalgism" /></p><p><strong>@technostalgism</strong></p><p>The Sony ICF-2001D (ICF-2010) is a piece of Cold War espionage history. Released in 1985, its synchronous detection made it the ultimate tool for spies intercepting number stations and DXers hunting weak signals. It still puts modern radios to shame today.<br/>
<br/>
Did your family own one? Let me know in the comments.<br/>
#Sony #ICF2001D #ICF2010 #Shortwave #Radio</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/649511647_2581668275562796_4270578688493732872_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_p360x360_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=102&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg0NzcyMzQwNTczOTM0MjEzMQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjY0MHgxMTM2LnNkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=-rMAEJTZBb8Q7kNvwFhORNw&amp;_nc_oc=Ado2uIGeV5n3bOBcieA5Av5ZHDglJHHt-h7T88WAdyntGrZIgiU4ShmnB0Kzv8vK3Gw&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=lUCi0V0oIzZL0N8geRpueQ&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyTK6tysEWSft9EQsG-N52kBkHQVsCgncWBtBE7aVt4iw&amp;oe=69C9B824" alt="Instagram billede fra @technostalgism" /></p><p><strong>@technostalgism</strong></p><p>The Sony ICF-2001D (ICF-2010) is a piece of Cold War espionage history. Released in 1985, its synchronous detection made it the ultimate tool for spies intercepting number stations and DXers hunting weak signals. It still puts modern radios to shame today.<br/>
<br/>
Did your family own one? Let me know in the comments.<br/>
#Sony #ICF2001D #ICF2010 #Shortwave #Radio</p>]]></content:encoded>
