    <item>
      <title>The Sony PS-F9 “Flamingo” is the turntable cool kids would need today. Flats are...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DTXndDpjNU3/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/612611227_1541972823756285_5531819398431968813_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_p360x360_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=102&amp;ig_cache_key=MzgwNzY4NTUzMDU2MjEyMzA2Mw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjY0MHgxMTM2LnNkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=nIqgEajpSMAQ7kNvwEdmJnm&amp;_nc_oc=AdreFA0PLPvzyW3kPvXEIWYNqhIDat8b65KPkxTiF_tD3JuSVOloe-DmfGsmDy-_5QM&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=lUCi0V0oIzZL0N8geRpueQ&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyMGuFRqKmICXnY_fIyxxXlfAKCJprlmzp8zZybjtl0ig&amp;oe=69C9A91A" alt="Instagram billede fra @technostalgism" /></p><p><strong>@technostalgism</strong></p><p>The Sony PS-F9 “Flamingo” is the turntable cool kids would need today. Flats are smaller, listen via headphones, no need for external preamps. Just a simple, gorgeous turntable. And don’t tell me about the Soundburger! Who wants a record played by a greasy burger that can’t be stood upside to marvel at the record? <br/>
<br/>
Sony got it right, just a few decades too early.<br/>
.<br/>
.<br/>
.<br/>
#sony #psf9 #turntable #hifi #analogaudio</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/612611227_1541972823756285_5531819398431968813_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_p360x360_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=102&amp;ig_cache_key=MzgwNzY4NTUzMDU2MjEyMzA2Mw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjY0MHgxMTM2LnNkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=nIqgEajpSMAQ7kNvwEdmJnm&amp;_nc_oc=AdreFA0PLPvzyW3kPvXEIWYNqhIDat8b65KPkxTiF_tD3JuSVOloe-DmfGsmDy-_5QM&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=lUCi0V0oIzZL0N8geRpueQ&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyMGuFRqKmICXnY_fIyxxXlfAKCJprlmzp8zZybjtl0ig&amp;oe=69C9A91A" alt="Instagram billede fra @technostalgism" /></p><p><strong>@technostalgism</strong></p><p>The Sony PS-F9 “Flamingo” is the turntable cool kids would need today. Flats are smaller, listen via headphones, no need for external preamps. Just a simple, gorgeous turntable. And don’t tell me about the Soundburger! Who wants a record played by a greasy burger that can’t be stood upside to marvel at the record? <br/>
<br/>
Sony got it right, just a few decades too early.<br/>
.<br/>
.<br/>
.<br/>
#sony #psf9 #turntable #hifi #analogaudio</p>]]></content:encoded>
